description: Dept. of Elections - Elected Mr. R. M. Priyantha Rukman Ratnayaka as a member of the Pallepola P/S - Mr. Susantha Gamini Gunasinghe as a member of the Kalutara P/S - Mr. Seema Hewage Kusman De Silva as the Chairman and Mr. Udatiyawalage Sumith Nishantha and Mr. Dodangoda Arachchige Piyasena as members of the Beruwala P/S
